        <h1>About This Project</h1>
        <p>Learn about the Football Jersey Showcase Platform - its purpose, technical implementation, and the technologies behind it.</p>
    </section>

    <main>
        <section class="section">
            <h2>Project Overview</h2>
            <p>The Football Jersey Showcase Platform is a comprehensive web application designed to celebrate and document the rich history and artistic evolution of football jerseys from clubs and national teams worldwide. This project serves as both an educational resource for football enthusiasts and a demonstration of cloud infrastructure deployment capabilities.</p>
            
            <p>Football jerseys are more than just sportswear - they represent cultural identity, historical moments, and design innovation. From the iconic yellow of Brazil to the red and black stripes of AC Milan, each jersey tells a unique story. This platform aims to preserve and share these stories with the global football community.</p>

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>Project Purpose</strong>
                <p>This website was developed as part of the ICT171 - Introduction to Server Environments and Architectures course at Murdoch University. The project demonstrates proficiency in cloud infrastructure deployment, Linux server administration, web development, and technical documentation.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h2>Technical Implementation</h2>
            
            <h3>Infrastructure</h3>
            <p>This website is deployed using <strong>Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS)</strong> on Microsoft Azure cloud platform. The deployment follows industry best practices for security, scalability, and reliability.</p>

            <table class="project-table">
                <tr>
                    <th>Component</th>
                    <th>Details</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Cloud Provider</strong></td>
                    <td>Microsoft Azure</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Virtual Machine</strong></td>
                    <td>ict171-vm (Ubuntu Server)</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Location</strong></td>
                    <td>UAE North Data Center</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Public IP</strong></td>
                    <td>20.233.33.117</td>
