                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Web Server</strong></td>
                    <td>Apache HTTP Server</td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <h3>Technology Stack</h3>
            <div class="tech-grid">
                <div class="tech-card">
                    <h4>Frontend</h4>
                    <p>HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript for responsive, modern web design</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tech-card">
                    <h4>Web Server</h4>
                    <p>Apache HTTP Server for reliable content delivery</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tech-card">
                    <h4>Cloud Platform</h4>
                    <p>Microsoft Azure IaaS for scalable infrastructure</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tech-card">
                    <h4>Operating System</h4>
                    <p>Ubuntu Linux for secure server environment</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3>Key Features</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Responsive Design:</strong> Fully optimized for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices</li>
                <li><strong>Static Architecture:</strong> Fast loading times and enhanced security through static HTML/CSS/JS</li>
                <li><strong>Clean Navigation:</strong> Intuitive menu system for easy browsing</li>
                <li><strong>Visual Design:</strong> Jersey representations using CSS gradients and modern styling</li>
                <li><strong>Comprehensive Coverage:</strong> Multiple sections covering different leagues and competitions</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Security Measures</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Firewall configuration (UFW) restricting unnecessary ports</li>
                <li>Regular system updates and security patches</li>
                <li>Proper file permissions and ownership</li>
                <li>SSL/TLS encryption (HTTPS implementation)</li>
                <li>Secure SSH access with key-based authentication</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h2>Development Process</h2>
            <p>The development of this platform followed a structured approach:</p>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>Phase 1: Planning & Design</strong>
                <p>Conceptualized the project scope, selected appropriate technologies, and designed the website architecture and visual style.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>Phase 2: Infrastructure Setup</strong>
                <p>Provisioned Azure virtual machine, configured Ubuntu Linux, installed and configured Apache web server, and implemented security measures.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>Phase 3: Development</strong>
                <p>Created HTML pages, designed CSS styling, implemented responsive layouts, and developed jersey visual representations.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>Phase 4: Deployment</strong>
                <p>Deployed website files to production server, configured DNS settings, tested accessibility, and implemented SSL/TLS certificates.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>Phase 5: Documentation</strong>
                <p>Created comprehensive technical documentation in GitHub, recorded video demonstration, and prepared final project report.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

