        <section class="section">
            <h2>Future Enhancements</h2>
            <p>Potential improvements and features for future versions of this platform:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Database Integration:</strong> Implement MySQL or PostgreSQL for dynamic content management</li>
                <li><strong>User Contributions:</strong> Allow users to submit their own jersey collections and stories</li>
                <li><strong>Search Functionality:</strong> Add advanced search and filtering options</li>
                <li><strong>Interactive Timeline:</strong> Visual timeline showing jersey evolution over decades</li>
                <li><strong>Comparison Tool:</strong> Side-by-side jersey comparison feature</li>
                <li><strong>API Integration:</strong> Connect with football statistics APIs for live data</li>
                <li><strong>Multi-language Support:</strong> Internationalization for global audience</li>
                <li><strong>Community Features:</strong> Forums, ratings, and discussion boards</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

